Neutral_Files: .csv/.xlsx for result tables, param sweeps, optimum sets
.json/.xml for final workflow definitions or HPC job logs
Metadata: Workflow version, HPC job ID, user, date/time, scenario name
Analysis type (DOE, MDAO, robust optimization, reliability-based design, etc.)

Process_and_Quality: CMMI references for orchestrated solver usage

Parameter_Sweeps: Input variables, boundary ranges, incremental steps
Optimization_Results: Best design sets, objective values, constraint violations
Job_Logs: Execution times, solver calls, concurrency usage
Error messages, warnings, HPC cluster reports
Final_Design_or_Solution: Chosen param combination, geometry ID, performance summary
Trade_Off_Analyses: Comparative plots, multi-run data for decision-making
